{"tid":1447173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人心口好大壓力,透唔到氣","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:14.000Z","uid":52985,"like":53,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a622a52c22a2b99f9765f4cde3ff84c903734704","tid":1447173,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇LIVE愈睇愈嬲<br />\n而家心入面一直浮現2隻字<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">報仇</span></span><br />\n但我希望大家真係好好考慮下下一步點做<br />\n<br />\n擒贼先擒王?<br />\n將路易16送上斷頭台?<br />\n定再搞冇限期大罷工<br />\n但今次7合1<br />\n將機場變成只可入境不可出境<br />\n<br />\n請大家記住<br />\n每一個行動都要時間宣傳<br />\n今日我地犧牲左好多好多<br />\n但我地可以利用今日既犧牲換到乜野<br />\n就取決於我地之後既行動"},{"pid":"d1ee5551d7301628ebc3b63ecce037797b6c5bb7","tid":1447173,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77dZi0D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77dZi0D.jpg&h=fefe4073&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c2faa195e1899f4ab2f37a901ed4cbca7037c46","tid":1447173,"uid":92340,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">贼</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"773e274d62423e1f198f9af767752ded79d3921a","tid":1447173,"uid":52985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5c2faa195e1899f4ab2f37a901ed4cbca7037c46","tid":1447173,"uid":92340,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">贼</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"SORRY因為唔識打個擒字<br />\n所以GOOGLE SEARCH : 賊先 王<br />\n出左個結果就COPY左落黎<br />\n冇留意真心SORRY"},{"pid":"9f2456a4af406afa018cbfceaa02fce94669910a","tid":1447173,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as