g":"政府絕對唔會讓步 讓一細步都唔得 因為佢哋唔可以俾你成功 因為只要成功左一次個無力感就會消失<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cEwyhS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cEwyhS</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家睇返好耐之前既呢個POST<br />\n大家而家身上有好大既無力感<br />\n係因為政府製造出黎<br />\n希望令大家絕望<br />\n絕望會令大家懷疑自己,令人放棄<br />\n所以大家一定唔可以比政府得逞"},{"pid":"cd2c3f31e951752a0d062115d6547eff60d10966","tid":1447173,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76c752d5a8623b69ceefc1d754f6ed1aa5b5b7e","tid":1447173,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"天佑義士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民抗爭 背水一戰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對港鐵不合作運動全民跳閘</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.勇武轉入地下打狗<br />\n2.和理非要癱瘓機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為受傷被捕兄弟討回公道</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線太多手足比捉 一定要升級癱瘓機場 全民打狗 選擇一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"525101240281f0e0adf78fdd7cf4a7e85f1f0244","tid":1447173,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"好撚嬲"},{"pid":"823864868138ce6520d5f6214a6d25cfa5a7a415","tid":1447173,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼, 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\